Procedure to add an image file in Readme.md: - 
===================================================
Method 1: Drag and drop image file to Readme.md
-----------
I. Click the pen icon to edit Readme.md file.
II. Drag and drop the image into the edit box.
III. Click the “Commit changes” button to save the image.

Method 2:  Markdown Syntax
--------------
The syntax looks like: ![Alt text](image link)
Add the above line in Readme.md file.
The syntax starts with !, the alt text is wrapped in the brackets [], and the image link is
wrapped in the parentheses.
This method is mainly used when the image to be used is saved somewhere in the repository.

Example: ![alt text](https://github.com/[username]/[reponame]/blob/[branch]/image.jpg?raw=true)
